Your method `mostrarInformacionEntry` is reading the fields of one JSON array entry. Your problem is, that this method isn&#39;t creating a new model per entry. Instead it assigns the read value `dc:identifier` to the class variable `ID`. This is done for all entries in the array. An entry overwrites the saved ID of the previous entry. At the end you create a model with the ID of the last loaded entry. But you should create a model for each entry.


You need a custom entry class/POJO:
```
